duckbotos-browseros (0.1.0) stable; urgency=medium

  * Initial DuckBotOS release.
    - Ubuntu 24.04 Noble base
    - Hermes v0.17 "Reach" agent mode
    - OpenClaw gateway + duckbot-memory brain plugin
    - DuckBot RAG brain (4-tier CoALA memory, MCP tools)
    - LM Studio headless server (localhost:1234)
    - BrowserOS as default browser
    - Weston + Chromium kiosk (fullscreen agent desktop)
    - Session picker for Hermes/OpenClaw/Hybrid mode selection
    - NVIDIA GPU support (CUDA acceleration)
    - DuckBot RAG brain with FSRS spaced repetition

